# Portfolio Rebuild — Project Standards

This project rebuilds lisawilkins.com from Figma Sites into a coded Astro + Tailwind CSS site deployed to Netlify.

Full plan: `/Users/lisawilkins/.cursor/plans/portfolio_rebuild_astro_b94db9e2.plan.md`

## Design References

- **Live site:** https://www.lisawilkins.com
- **Figma Site file (primary):** https://www.figma.com/site/xUxdmk3djYdKXqXvsjBW7t/2025Portfolio?node-id=0-1&t=uqDSPTB7bVjsXbIY-1
  - Shows all 3 pages at desktop, tablet, and mobile breakpoints
  - This is the file that builds the live site — use it as the visual source of truth

## Rebuild Rules

- **Replicate exactly.** Match every visible aspect: fonts, type sizes and weights, colors, spacing, layout, images, copy, and links. Approximations are not acceptable.
- **Use the design system.** Tokens are defined in `src/styles/globals.css`. Use them — do not use hardcoded hex values or generic Tailwind utilities where a token exists.
- **Ask before guessing.** If a section's layout or visual treatment cannot be confirmed from the live URL, ask for a Figma link, screenshot, or description before proceeding.

## Stack

- Framework: Astro 5 (static)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4
- Fonts: Barlow (body, 400/600/800) + Alegreya (headings) via `@fontsource`
- Hosting: Netlify via GitHub

## Page Structure

| Route | File |
|---|---|
| `/` | `src/pages/index.astro` |
| `/projects-nbcapp` | `src/pages/projects-nbcapp.astro` |
| `/projects-puf` | `src/pages/projects-puf.astro` |
| `#connect` | `src/components/HelloSection.astro` (anchor, not a separate page) |

## Key Files

- Design tokens: `src/styles/globals.css`
- Layout wrapper: `src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro`
- Nav (global): `src/components/Header.astro`
- Footer (global): `src/components/Footer.astro`
- Hello/bio section: `src/components/HelloSection.astro`
- Images: `public/images/` (organized by page: `home/`, `nbc/`, `strategy/`, `og/`)
